Package: xcmsVisGUI
Title: Interactive Raw LC-MS Viewer (Shiny)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Jan", "Stanstrup", email = "stanstrup@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A local Shiny desktop application for interactively visualising raw
    LC-MS data on the RforMassSpectrometry stack (Spectra, MsExperiment, xcms).
    Features asynchronous file reading, file inclusion control, rich filtering,
    multiple EICs per file, click-to-spectrum, 2D/3D maps, and
    publication-quality export.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://stanstrup.github.io/xcmsVisGUI, https://github.com/stanstrup/xcmsVisGUI
BugReports: https://github.com/stanstrup/xcmsVisGUI/issues
